juniE2Registry.description: Juniper second generation E-series product family system-specific object identification values. This module defines AutonomousType (OID) values for all the physical entity types (entPhysicalVendorType). This module will be updated whenever a new type of module or other hardware becomes available in second generation E-series systems.

e2Chassis.name: e2Chassis
e2Chassis.description: The vendor type ID for a second generation E-series chassis. This identifies an 'overall' physical entity for any second generation E-series system.
